Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}八點十分 勉強趕上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不見了 這下傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣的話就進不了家門了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}轉學第一天就弄丟鑰匙 真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我真沒用 實在太沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你早啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早...早啊 話說 妳弄丟鑰匙了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 為什麼你會知道啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 因為聽到妳在碎碎念啦 如果不介意的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你願意幫我找嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}果然這座島上的人都很親切呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奶奶說「四島列島是人情之島 無須擔心」真的是這樣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我昨天才剛搬來這座久奈島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳是在找這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝你 謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.25,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晶也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}人...人在天上飛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂 我說妳 給我乖乖在停留所降落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好厲害 好厲害 有人從天空飛下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我叫做倉科明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好像是轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你怎麼知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學在找鑰匙的時候自己講的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}連我的名字都知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 我剛剛做過自我介紹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一大早就這麼情緒高漲 還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是日向晶也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她是鳶澤美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們兩個都是久奈浜學院的二年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 我也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說啊 趕快去學校比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個禮拜是各務老師值勤喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對吼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.61,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}各務老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雖然她是健康老師 但也負責生活指導
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}遲到的話 就會有可怕的懲罰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有懲罰嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}聽說老師會靠自己的人脈網路蒐集學生的黑歷史 並將其公開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼會 作為一個人 這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好了啦 快一點 要飛囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}停留所在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了 就飛過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晶也呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我會跑步過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 要怎麼飛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳穿著我們學校的制服 就表示妳應該聽過反重力鞋的說明了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}反重力鞋... 啊 是說這個鞋子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來 妳是沒用過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真沒辦法 那妳就和我一起飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂 美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}周遭沒問題 也沒有禁止飛行的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 要出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來 快點抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晶也也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一 二 要飛囉喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不行 絕對會掉下去 要掉下去了 要掉下去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請妳不要睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我醒著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}只要反重力鞋的電源開著 就絕對不會掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 所以就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好好享受空中漫步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...在飛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有這個鞋子的話 好像真的哪裡都能飛過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哪裡都能去...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還有三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哦 那傢伙竟然用飛的來 真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼這個坡要用跑的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我哪知道 這就是規則 我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}五 四 三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 看來今天也沒人遲到 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早安啊 各務老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這位就是那個很嚴格又很可怕的老師嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 喂 這種話一般會在本人面前說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳是轉學生倉科同學吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我就是嚴格又可怕的各務葵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}能請妳跟我來一趟辦公室嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}果然是我們班的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這座久奈島是我爸爸的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以我小時候曾來過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}現在因爸爸的工作關係搬家到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就在我想著「大海好美 天空好高啊~」的時候就跌倒了 把鑰匙...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.58,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}能請妳先到位子上坐好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}從教室也能看到大海和天空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好了啦 妳快坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 鳶澤美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}同學 剛才真是謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:29.80,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}太近了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 日向晶也同學也是同一班的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}正好 鳶澤和日向 就拜託你們當倉科的指導員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.56,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晶也 今天提早放學了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 今天終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要做什麼呢? 要吃什麼呢? 有無限的可能正向我襲來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總覺得鳶澤同學的情緒和早上完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}有低血壓 所以早上大概都是半夢半醒的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}過中午後簡直就判若兩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}連身為她朋友的我都為她感到不安了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我只是忠實地照自己的方式在過生活而已唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}換個想法 這還真是讓人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 我叫青柳{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}窓{\r\blur2}果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如果接下來沒事的話 我們來練習用反重力鞋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}也是指導員 就過來陪我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了 我會去的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 指導員是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}規定上 反重力鞋的新手 一定要有一個指導員負責教導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}和我都有取得指導員的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 那 那就是教練的意思囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請多多指教 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天我因為當值日生 沒辦法和妳一起上學 好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}回去的時候要讓我好好補充美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊的成份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天不行 因為我得當這孩子的指導員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了 我也陪你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是一年A班的有坂真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}該說是美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊的下屬嗎 還是說是僕人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說回來 倉科學姊會打電動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}PSQ? 4DS?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 還是妳是桌遊或手遊派的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}順帶一提 我不管哪個都很會玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要用什麼來決勝負呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.26,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}可以開始做反重力鞋的說明了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}反重力鞋 Anti Gravity Shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是在發現能反重力的神奇粒子後做出來的產物 這妳知道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這四島列島 是被允許能使用反重力鞋作為交通手段的特別區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}從數年前開始 其也被認同為一種上學方式了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喵 感覺好死板啊 說明就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 試著墊起兩腳的腳尖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對 接著只要自己抓準時機 對著鞋子說Fly 它就會慢慢飄起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}預 備~ Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}動起來了 它動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...在飛 我在飛唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科學姊看起來很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是啊 如果那樣亂揮動手的話 它馬上就會開始搖晃...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}平衡突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.21,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}放心吧 讓人安全著陸也是反重力鞋機能之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一開始大家就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 今天就到此為止 來去吃烏龍麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:17.57,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}烏龍麵...嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對 名產四島烏龍麵 肚子都餓扁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天的配菜要選什麼好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想想喵...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.54,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們先飛過去了 你們趕快跟上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要飛囉喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}走吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 原來這家烏龍麵店是有坂同學家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哇 是飛魚先生 我最喜歡飛魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這邊的烏龍麵用了美味的豬顎骨湯頭 很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}豬顎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 烏龍麵送來之前 我們來玩聞名於久奈島的美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊猜謎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我才不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來玩吧 我想更了解大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 第一題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊的興趣是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}答案是在奶奶親傳的糠床製作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 第二題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊的三圍是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是我的三圍再分別加上11 7 12
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼妳會知道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來 讓妳久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一直以來承蒙您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哇 看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小心不要燙到舌頭囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊 明天我們一起上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳們兩個感情真的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今天真是謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}鳶澤同學飛的姿勢相當漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但我卻完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不用那麼在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}只要接下來慢慢練習就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 倉科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不用那麼沮喪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 是...是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}剛才啊 我一個人飛的時候非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是才飛一下子就變得搖搖晃晃 馬上就掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以啊 明天起也請盡情地訓練我吧 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}飛都飛不好 真是沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在天上飛真的很舒服 好期待明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}鳶澤教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}日向教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}接下來也請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}隔壁有人搬家過來...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哎呀 這麼慘的新手我還真沒見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂 妳要放鬆點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 我放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但妳感覺更緊繃了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}被風吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要趕快追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是會給人添麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來還有很長的路要走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}已經完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說 妳這姿勢是怎樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不知道為什麼 保持這個姿勢會比較穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這傢伙搞不好是個稀有角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是路人在打架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得應該不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來去偷看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}特地來挑戰我還輸掉 真是丟人現眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以我才說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}竟然想挑戰我佐藤院麗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這就像在太平洋中挑戰鯊魚一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雖然搞不清楚 不過好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 那個人是{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}窓{\r\blur2}果的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這什麼狀況? 在單挑嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}能夠在Flying Circus戰勝我佐藤院麗子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在久奈浜學院裡根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Flying Circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是使用反重力鞋進行的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 妳是第一次聽說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 那依照約定 我就收下久奈浜學院的「院」字囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}從今天開始 你們就叫「沒有院字的久奈浜學」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯獨這個...!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}學校的名字會改變嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 妳給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科學姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這下糟了 我才不要就這樣被叫久奈浜學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 所以我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Come back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}笨蛋 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 雖然我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但 如果我在那個Flying Circus中贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}可以把「院」字還給我們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼我要藏起來啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.57,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是剛轉學到久奈浜學院的倉科明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是場外亂鬥啊 真是興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也就是說 妳想挑戰我吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳對Flying Circus就這麼有自信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 我才剛知道這東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}穿著反重力鞋自己一個人飛 今天也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳要開玩笑也給我有點限度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我才沒在開玩笑 我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}既然如此 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳說到這份上了 我就陪妳過一手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}非常感謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}給我等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個人可是高藤學園的學生喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}高藤學園可是以Flying Circus出名的學校喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}事情變得有趣起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 問題不在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練 請妳教我Flying Circus吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Flying Circus是在被浮標包圍 單邊300公尺的正方形海面上進行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一對一進行比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在十分鐘內得到較多分的人獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}得分的方式有兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}摸到對方的背後 或是按照順序摸四個浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她真的是第一次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就配合新手 把浮標減少到兩個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽時間就減半 五分鐘就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}只要拿到一分 就算妳贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 紫苑同學 你來當裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後 妳就負責當指揮者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(1155,975)}{\blur2}Second
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}指揮者是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(855,975)}{\blur2}Second
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是指在地面上負責下指示的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼教練 就麻煩妳給我指示了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}將青色的祝福賜給吾之羽翼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好了 別發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要從空中那個一號浮標開始出發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}誰知道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}讓妳久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs40\pos(960,975)\blur2}Set
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我就不客氣地先拿下一分囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佐藤院 一分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂 妳們在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如你所見 在比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉...倉科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個是高藤學園的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽用的反重力鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼要和那種人比賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為她擅自和別人吵了與自己無關的架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}蛤? 聽不懂妳在說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 讓我來當指揮者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(1152,975)}{\blur2}Second
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學 聽得到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}日向教練
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}首先要阻擋對手的前進路線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就像足球的守門員那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}把雙手撐開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳以為這種防守能擋得住我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她...她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後變換方向 去碰她的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總之 繞到她身後去碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}背後是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佐藤院 兩分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不知道Flying Circus就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}連飛都飛成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也還真是被小看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佐藤院 九分 九比零...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}果然還是不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好像連要拿到一分都很困難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼我要收下第十分囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳就乖乖投降如何啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我才不會投降 久奈浜學院的「院」字 就由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我絕對會拿到一分給妳看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦 她是不服輸的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}接下來按照我說的去行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}講什麼悄悄話啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 我要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是現在 把雙腳併起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就那樣朝著天空上升
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哎呀 是想要慶祝我的勝利嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是現在 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}背後 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}才不會讓妳得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}被躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還有十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}到此為止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}讓一無是處的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}此時此刻 展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Air Kick Turn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎...怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}成...成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我成功拿到一分了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}得...得分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我叫倉科明日香
Comment: 0,0:22:15.54,0:23:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.76,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得我應該不會想再來第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}特大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}
